        "urlToImage": "https://sportshub.cbsistatic.com/i/r/2022/07/01/e917d9d8-f5ef-426f-ac18-4b2bfc244a03/thumbnail/1200x675/300d05d2e1906d9b118e5accd456c2f9/lavine-1g.jpg",
        "publishedAt": "2022-07-02T18:13:00Z",
        "content": "NBA free agency is under way, and it's moving along at a rapid pace. As of Thursday evening, teams and players could officially begin negotiating new contracts. However, NBA fans didn't have to wait … [+1033 chars]"
